 offering new products  services our entrepreneurial philosophy encourages a diversity of people products  services needed to flourish at the local level by being successful at the local branch level we have been able to grow consistently   about beacon roofing supply north americas largest publicly traded roofing distributor over  locations across  us states and  canadian provinces a fortune  company traded on the nasdaq stock exchange under the symbol becn open an account apply for a cash or credit account with beacon our customer financial services cfs department gives our contractor customers convenient access to the lines of credit and terms they need to be competitive in the marketplace open your account online account management the easiest and fastest way to manage your account  online access anytime anywhere save time by scheduling future payments download billing information into your business accounting software manage your account build your career apply for a job with beacon roofing supply being north americas largest publicly traded roofing distributor we are always recruiting for the best talent   view our current job openings becn regional brands alabama roofing supply american building  roofing atlantic building products applicators sales beacon roofing supply canada company beacon sales best distributing bj supply cassady pierce coastal metal service dealers choice enercon products ford wholesale   fox brothers company groupe bédard jga beacon lyftym building products mcclure johnston mississippi roofing supply north coast roofing systems pacific supply posislope procoat systems quality roofing suppl rci roofing supply roofing and insulation supply ris   ris roofing supply roof depot roofing supply group southern roof center statewide wholesale structural materials the roof center west end roofing siding  windows wholesale roofing supply woodfeathers inc corporate headquarters  huntmar park drive suite  herndon va  ph  fx  copyright  beacon roofing