tates and  canadian provinces profile beacon roofing supply inc is the second largest and largest publicly traded distributor of residential and nonresidential roofing materials in the united states and canada we also distribute complementary building products including siding windows specialty exterior building products insulation and waterproofing systems for residential and nonresidential building exteriors we operate over  branches in  states and  canadian provinces we are a leading distributor of roofing materials and complementary building products in key markets across the united states and canada our branchbased operating model allows us to capitalize on our local personnels extensive knowledge of each market served in this way we can tailor product offerings and services to customer needs while benefiting from the purchasing information technology credit and other resources and efficiencies of a national distribution organization   we provide our customers with a comprehensive array of valueadded services which distinguishes us from our competition we have earned a reputation for excellent employees professionalism and highquality service     investor relations contact joseph nowicki executive vice president  chief financial officer beacon roofing supply inc jnowickibeaconroofingsupplycom tel   press releases jul   beacon roofing supply to announce third quarter  earnings on august   jun   beacon roofing supply to participate in the william blair th annual growth stock conference view all press releases » events  presentations aug   at  pm et beacon roofing supply third quarter  earnings conference call listen to webcast view all events  presentations » investor relations profile management corporate governance code violation hotline press releases events  presentations annual reports sec filings key ratios stock performance historic stock lookup investment calculator investor faqs contact us nasdaq stock quote becn       volume  jul    pm et   about beacon